  <official_title>Pilot Study to Assess the Effects of Vitamin D Supplementation on the Number of Regulatory FoxP3+ T Cells in the Gastrointestinal Mucosa in Healthy Women and Men: Step 3 in the Austrian Diabetes Prevention Programme</official_title>
